# Archo, Republic of Dagestan

}}
Archo (; ) is a rural locality (a selo) in Akhvakhsky District, Republic of Dagestan, Russia. The population was 347 as of 2010.
Geography
Archo is located 3&nbsp;km west of Karata (the district's administrative centre) by road. Mashtada is the nearest rural locality.
